          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for study, recitation and consultation during the performance of different Hindu rites and rituals, possibly those related to the Agnihotra or fire ceremony, and the rules and regulations (Hindu law, Dharma) associated with them. Includes various mantras to be recited by a officiating priest (agnihotṛ) such as those ending, idam na mama.</summary>
